import React, { useEffect, useState } from "react"; import { useNavigate } from "react-router-dom"; function Ranking() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const [rankingData, setRankingData] = useState({}); useEffect(() => { fetch("/countrys_ranking") .then((res) => res.json()) .then((data) => setRankingData(data.countrys)); }, []); return ( <> {Object.keys(rankingData).map((id) => ( ))}
Rank Name Points Previous Points +/- Position
{id} navigate(`/country/${id})`)} className="item country" style={{ backgroundColor: `rgba(${rankingData[id].color[0]}, ${rankingData[id].color[1]}, ${rankingData[id].color[2]}, 0.5)`, color: "#fff", }} > {rankingData[id].name} {rankingData[id].points} {rankingData[id].prev_points} {rankingData[id].diff_points} {/* % if country > countrys[country]["prev_ranking"] % */} {/* { countrys[country]["diff_ranking"] } */} {/* % elif country < countrys[country]["prev_ranking"] % */} {/* { countrys[country]["diff_ranking"] } */} {/* % elif country == countrys[country]["prev_ranking"]% */} {/* % endif % */}
); } export default Ranking;
